{"tid":1352271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對準目標政權 香港人無得再輸","createTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T19:49:19.000Z","uid":219211,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e9de0a0c43acc09161eab33481ce23ac282b02eb","tid":1352271,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:11.000Z","msg":"去到宜家呢個地步無得再退，再做其他運動亦只會消耗我軍意志，人手。<br />\n元朗件事全世界人都嬲。知大家好想報仇。<br />\n但理性諗下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打贏又點？會比人拉幾多人？打黑社會對我地無好處</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要贏共產黨。<br />\n佢地最叻就係搞呢啲內鬥。大家都知班黑社會同政府有關，明知係局點解仲要去？<br />\n<br />\n對準目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奪回政權</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後想講:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">今次只許勝利</span></span>"},{"pid":"121c5af0671187d42925ae638a8d36051d396bf0","tid":1352271,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a267823d00eb08f66d464f248059868818620013","tid":1352271,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"咁即係入唔入元朗先"},{"pid":"ce602c2987bd2e93638e4fd70607524adeefb08b","tid":1352271,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"59a3ba398fbb324cfef6060661650ce035c17921","tid":1352271,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a267823d00eb08f66d464f248059868818620013","tid":1352271,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"咁即係入唔入元朗先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"為啖氣，值唔值？<br />\n邊樣重要啲？"},{"pid":"bafb04edd791e8975a0b68f7fd5b7e9b96fa4b1f","tid":1352271,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:14:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pi